doc.after: Since its inception Virgin Blue had sponsored many sporting teams in a bid to promote its brand In February 2007 Virgin Blue signed a two year sponsorship deal with NRL team the South Sydney Rabbitohs The Rabbitohs are the first rugby league team Virgin Australia has sponsored 43 Boeing 737 800 VH VUA has slight changes to its livery to commemorate this sponsorship The Australian flag held by the Virgin Girl is replaced by the Rabbitohs flag Virgin Australia is also the official sponsor of the National Basketball League NBL and the title sponsor of NBL team the Brisbane Bullets
